Job Description
World leading Engineering & Construction firm within the Energy, Oil & Gas, and Petrochemical Industry is currently seeking a Head of Estimation & Proposals to be responsible for their directing all estimation and proposals activity across the Middle East and North Africa.
Head of Estimation & Proposals
Competitive Package
Based in the Middle East
JOB DESCRIPTION
•Provide functional support and responsibility for multiple projects
•Coordinating multiple estimates simultaneously as well as review responsibility for multiple or large estimates
•Establishing and maintaining an estimating department evaluation procedures
•Establish and maintaining department resource library
•Recruitment and development of all estimating personnel
•Assisting operations to select projects to bid
•Establishing and coordinating bidding schedule
•Reviewing project to develop win strategy
•Reviewing pricing and scheduling
•Establishing and maintaining relationships with owners, consultants, subs and suppliers
•Reviewing project cost reports
•Developing and maintaining estimating systems and procedures
•Arranging and managing bid turnover to operations
•Establishing district rate files for labor, equipment and materials
•Reviewing final cost report with project team and develop for historical information
•Conducting post-bid review
•Assisting and/or leading in proposal preparation, presentation and securing new work
•Assisting and preparing fee and risk analysis
•Responsible for the management of all aspects of the estimating department
•Responsible for ensuring all activities conform to IEC procedures
EDUCATION and/or EXPERIENCE
•Engineering or Construction related degree preferred, but will consider a Technical college certification or trade background with subsequent experience
•Advanced knowledge of estimating strategies and techniques within the Oil & Gas sector
•Thorough understanding of construction, contracts and terminology
•Minimum of 10 years experience in the Oil, Gas, Power and Process industry in estimating, proposals, project execution or business development, preferably in the MENA region
SOFTWARE EXPERIENCE
Estimating Software Microsoft Office Suite (Word, Excel, Visio, and PowerPoint)
SKILLS AND ATTRIBUTES
•Good planning and organizational skills
•Well-developed interpersonal and communication skills
•Professional appearance and manner
